DESCRIPTION:“Picture abhi baaki hai mere dost.”\n\nStep into the colourful world of Bollywood and create your own filmy poster! Join us for a dynamic collage-making workshop led by renowned filmmaker and producer\, Anand Tharaney. \n\nYou’ll dive into the rich visual language of Hindi cinema\, using iconic film stills and posters from MAP’s collection. You will also learn techniques to layer and blend elements that pay homage to the flamboyant aesthetics of the industry. Come express your love for cinema through art and discover the stories behind the images! \n\nWhile this workshop is fully booked\, we encourage you to visit MAP on November 30th and December 1st for a variety of exciting events and activities happening at Art is Life.
